https://www.reddit.com/r/dailyprogrammer/comments/shp28/4192012_challenge_41_easy/

Write a program that will accept a sentence as input and then output that
sentence surrounded by some type of an ASCII decoratoin banner.

Sample run:

Enter a sentence: So long and thanks for all the fish

Output

*****************************************
*                                       *
*  So long and thanks for all the fish  *
*                                       *
*****************************************
